        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2024-05-14 05:08:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: -Code-Review\n\nI discussed this with Peter and Oleg, and because el9.3 is passing builds, this may be a transient error related only to the el9.2 kernel, so is not a reason to block this patch.  If el9.2 is a target of interest then a separate patch can be landed to fix the issue.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "386cb715b8782f94132a31b3dc9565214717ae45",
      "author": {
