        "name": "James Simmons",
        "email": "jsimmons@infradead.org",
        "username": "jsimmons"
      },
      "date": "2024-05-21 15:10:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n> Patch Set 5: -Code-Review\n> \n> I discussed this with Peter and Oleg, and because el9.3 is passing builds, this may be a transient error related only to the el9.2 kernel, so is not a reason to block this patch.  If el9.2 is a target of interest then a separate patch can be landed to fix the issue.\n\nThis looks like the gcc bug - https://gcc.gnu.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=98503",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 5
    },
